{
  "texts": [
    "When we tested it with the same parameters used in the previous study on our lung cancer dataset, several artifacts were classified as true variants (Supplementary Table S3).",
    "As a result, we observed the F1-score of 0.13, which is not robust.",
    "We hypothesized that AI-based algorithms rather than rule-based approaches such as the \"at least 2 caller\" strategy can cope effectively with various DNA and sequencing data qualities affected by FFPE.",
    "Consistent with this hypothesis, we showed that FFPolish, which employs the machine learning algorithm logistic regression, can make better predictions than rule-based approaches.",
    "Even if an AI algorithm is outstanding, a decision should be explained before its performance can be trusted."
  ]
}